OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CSmoothy
OL,6,FPeter Smoothy, Age 99, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 19 July 2023
OL,10,FAmong a crew of 99 on a Tank Landing
OL,11,FShip that crossed the Channel on D-
OL,12,FDay, Peter Smoothy from Herne Bay was
OL,13,Fpart of the massive effort to drop
OL,14,Fvehicles onto the beaches in support
OL,15,Fof the landing soldiers.
OL,17,FHis vessel was designed to support
OL,18,Famphibious landings and went to Juno
OL,19,FBeach.
