OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CSmoothy
OL,6,FIt was carrying tanks on the inner
OL,7,Fdeck, lorries on the upper deck and
OL,8,Fhad about 200 people on board
OL,9,Fincluding drivers and crew.
OL,11,F"On D-Day we arrived on time when we
OL,12,Fwere supposed to be there, and we
OL,13,Ftowed a big flat ferry behind us going
OL,14,Fover," Mr Smoothy said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
