OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CSmoothy
OL,6,F"We anchored up and loaded some
OL,7,Fvehicles out through our doors onto
OL,8,Fthis big ferry because it would float
OL,9,Fin about three inches of water -
OL,10,Fmanaged to get that away to the shore
OL,11,Fwhich took I think about 15 vehicles
OL,12,Faltogether.
OL,14,F"They came back to do another one, but
OL,15,Fthe tide and the wind caught them and
OL,16,Fthey lost control of it in the end and
OL,17,Fthe carrier they were using blew into
OL,18,Fthe shore.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
