OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CSmoothy
OL,6,F"By then they were getting people out
OL,7,Fof the ship straight onto the beach
OL,8,Fthrough LST, landing ship tanks,
OL,9,Fthat's what they're called.
OL,11,F"People don't see very many of them
OL,12,Fbut they're the biggest ships that
OL,13,Fthey were using for the war carrying
OL,14,Fthe biggest amount of troops and
OL,15,Fvehicles."
OL,17,FMr Smoothy and his fellow comrades
OL,18,Fwere involved in carrying nearly 30
OL,19,Ftanks and about 45 vehicles.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
