OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Peter
OL,4,CSmoothy
OL,6,F"All the firing was going from our
OL,7,Fships behind us. We weren't very far
OL,8,Ffrom (HMS) Belfast actually.
OL,10,F"And we went round her bow before she
OL,11,Flet a full salvo go. I was in the
OL,12,Fstern of our ship and I thought I was
OL,13,Fgoing in the water.
OL,15,F"You can imagine when I go to see the
OL,16,FBelfast in London now that's where my
OL,17,Fmemories go. To that day in 1944."
